This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the computational tractability of the algorithms, which is related to algorithms and complexity (cs.AI). The algorithms presented in the paper rely on efficient data structures and optimization techniques, which are related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the control of dynamical systems, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the application of the algorithms to robotics, which is related to robotics (cs.RO).
